0 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">了另一种价值。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y2a7 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">像藏地大德米拉日巴尊者，<span class="_ _d"></span><span class="ls45">正是因为伯父、<span class="_ _d"></span><span class="ls3c">姑母的迫害，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y33 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls1c ws0">他才有了后来那么高的成就。由于他<span class="ls1d">们强夺了他的一切财</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y34 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">产，<span class="_ _6"></span>他为了报复才去学诛法，<span class="_ _6"></span>回来杀了很多人。<span class="_ _6"></span>造了如此罪</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y35 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">业之后，<span class="_ _8"></span>他从内心深处生起极大的后悔，<span class="_ _8"></span>觉得自己是世上最</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y36 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">大的恶人。<span class="_ _6"></span>为了忏悔，<span class="_ _6"></span>他经历种种苦行，<span class="_ _6"></span>最后获得了无上的</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y14e ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">证悟，成为历史上了不起的大成就者。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
